{"id": "1421435867402338375", "channel_id": "1421435867402338375", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "感谢各位守密人的支持！\n《忘却前夜》OST：畸变丰穰之种 已发布，欢迎收听、下载及分享。\n如果有基于OST的二次创作，也欢迎分享给我们！（二创请遵照同人规则，OST内容请勿商用）\n\n忘却前夜OST：畸变丰穰之种\n旧日的女王，被遗忘的女王，她依然在无边孤寂中等待。\n等待着她的血与种，被带向湮灭后的新世界。\n\n作曲：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n规划：B.I.A.V. Studio\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\nThank you for your support!\n\nMorimens OST: Seed of Grotesque Abundance was released today. \nWelcome everyone to listen, download and share. If you have secondary creations based on the OST, please also share them with us!\n (Please follow the rules of the fandom for secondary creations, and do not use the OST content for commercial purposes)\n\nMorimens OST: Seed of Grotesque Abundance\nThe queen of old, the forgotten queen, she waits still in boundless solitude. She waits for her blood and seed to be carried toward a new world, after annihilation.\n\nComposer：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\nPlanning：B.I.A.V. Studio", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T09:58:39.790000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "bow", "emoji_id": "1356053037159944473", "count": 14}, {"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1421435868064776233", "filename": "OST-250827.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2158236, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421435868064776233/OST-250827.jpg?ex=69ccec4f&is=69cb9acf&hm=7b347f0c640388ec094b639936ce25d0da950c28a7b36b987ccf71e0f8dd074d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1421435867402338375", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：畸变丰穰之种", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1421436246043000953", "channel_id": "1421435867402338375", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**01.在棺椁中重逢-Reunion in the Coffin-**\n\n她游离于记忆和过往之外，她穿过死和生的淤泥，静默地与你重逢。\n\nShe drifts beyond memory and the past, passing through the silt of death and life to be reunited with you in silence.", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T10:00:10.065000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1421436245434699836", "filename": "1.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1403139, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421436245434699836/1.jpg?ex=69cceca9&is=69cb9b29&hm=4ed93167c214c49cbc72c86ef19294b267a68820ec2302c69c233cbd39051c17&"}, {"id": "1421436245749403770", "filename": "1.-Reunion_in_the_Coffin-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 45097428, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421436245749403770/1.-Reunion_in_the_Coffin-.wav?ex=69cceca9&is=69cb9b29&hm=01dbecf235771bfa3ab5ec69c70b1f2f0c715aea5e090e0b5bf0745670836f68&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1421435867402338375", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：畸变丰穰之种", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1421436336618995793", "channel_id": "1421435867402338375", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**02.丰穰的末路-Abundance's End-**\n\n亚兰的子民行遍了大漠，他们生于此，他们长于此，他们注定要繁荣于此处，注定要消亡于此处。\n\nThe people of Aram have journeyed across the great desert. They were born here, they grew here, and they are destined to prosper and perish here.", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T10:00:31.660000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1421436335771619398", "filename": "2.-Abundances_End-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 30621396, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421436335771619398/2.-Abundances_End-.wav?ex=69ccecbf&is=69cb9b3f&hm=228b58553cde107e8684279735de50ae8e24c2f14c4198acb4524e3574dce5ba&"}, {"id": "1421436336703012986", "filename": "2.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1400265, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421436336703012986/2.jpg?ex=69ccecbf&is=69cb9b3f&hm=3deb9be92c819e5d27810a3c21cf18468e532b876858855bcd7eca5739163df4&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1421435867402338375", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：畸变丰穰之种", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1421436578168963113", "channel_id": "1421435867402338375", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**03.坠往黄沙-Falling into the Yellow Sands-**\n\n炽烈的太阳快要死去了，风裹挟砂砾将它熄灭。\n沉坠的太阳落下了，落向天与沙的交界。\n\nThe scorching sun is dying, and the wind, a tide of sand and grit, will soon extinguish it. \nThe sinking sun falls toward the boundary of sky and sand.", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T10:01:29.250000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1421436577263128698", "filename": "4.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1402058, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421436577263128698/4.jpg?ex=69ccecf9&is=69cb9b79&hm=a1d2a27ce9be0b5e8392351333ae80dcd84006579ccb02abca0dd6d6077117b6&"}, {"id": "1421436577799733278", "filename": "3.-Falling_into_the_Yellow_Sands-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 28550450, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421436577799733278/3.-Falling_into_the_Yellow_Sands-.wav?ex=69ccecf9&is=69cb9b79&hm=616a82dae19e9d91334f32d85f6307b9a735371318824a44c76c7c1679771597&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1421435867402338375", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：畸变丰穰之种", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1421436712701263884", "channel_id": "1421435867402338375", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**04.情热时分-Moment of Passion-**\n\n蜜酿已经斟满，贵客已经到场，请为勒姆瓦希带来新的种子，请尽情欢享浸透欲望的热情！\n\nThe mead has been poured, the honored guests have arrived. Please, bring new seeds to Remouahe! Please, indulge in the passion steeped in desire!", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T10:02:01.325000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1421436711744835705", "filename": "4.-Moment_of_Passion-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 43610484, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421436711744835705/4.-Moment_of_Passion-.wav?ex=69cced19&is=69cb9b99&hm=cfb0df527fa4b339d0548508896d2a839544f1886f33f121914a1f8f9816be54&"}, {"id": "1421436712286031952", "filename": "3.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1390820, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421436712286031952/3.jpg?ex=69cced19&is=69cb9b99&hm=3b4bb4046ff433ca29dd95a043a338a049154bb8a5eabfa8732b34172030f2d5&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1421435867402338375", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：畸变丰穰之种", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1421436922617921666", "channel_id": "1421435867402338375", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**05.繁衍，繁衍！-Reproduce! Procreate!-**\n\n引吭吧，起舞吧，当蜜和乳在火光旁交融。\n那终焉已愈发近了，以足攀援，以臂交缠，以颈倾吻——繁衍！繁衍！在母树的荫蔽之下，终有种嗣会获得垂怜！\n\nSing! Dance! As mead and milk mingle by the firelight, The End is drawing near. \nClimb with your feet, intertwine your arms, kiss each other's necks—Reproduce! Procreate! For under the protection of the Mother Tree, a remnant of our descendants will one day find mercy!", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T10:02:51.373000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1421436921900564620", "filename": "5.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1413406, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421436921900564620/5.jpg?ex=69cced4b&is=69cb9bcb&hm=049e630f4a74589bf8961547e669e3ef7aca9ba390fa5875b0e64666ea26337b&"}, {"id": "1421436922303221810", "filename": "5.-Reproduce_Procreate-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 42943108, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421436922303221810/5.-Reproduce_Procreate-.wav?ex=69cced4b&is=69cb9bcb&hm=efd3678cc908b68e62aa6cc9cc8d76f742ad615ac5f095dc7b2463331234dd2d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1421435867402338375", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：畸变丰穰之种", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1421437118256910376", "channel_id": "1421435867402338375", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**06.还于圣河-Returned to the Holy River-**\n\n好孩子，乖宝贝，圣河会安抚你夭折的啼哭，圣河会托抱你流逝的魂灵。\n\nGood child, my dear one, may the Holy River soothe your stillborn cries, may her gentle currents hold your fading soul.", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T10:03:38.017000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1421437116826652773", "filename": "6.-Returned_to_the_Holy_River-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 28545786, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421437116826652773/6.-Returned_to_the_Holy_River-.wav?ex=69cced79&is=69cb9bf9&hm=9b5df90e0d28b90cf92111de3994ba223b2dc1f961097d9f0bfc4529728ea255&"}, {"id": "1421437117715976212", "filename": "6.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1396648, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421437117715976212/6.jpg?ex=69cced79&is=69cb9bf9&hm=df98b14a043996c7d1be403173525d3b0e11bf03eed7b287e8f9b4589191a1d0&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1421435867402338375", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：畸变丰穰之种", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1421437317880610876", "channel_id": "1421435867402338375", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**07.她愿引颈-She Offers Her Neck-**\n\n无人铭记她的过往，无人知晓她的耳语。\n她贴近命定之人，呼吸织缠，形影相依。\n俯首，引颈。\n\nNo one remembers her past. No one knows her whispers. \nShe draws close to her fated one, her breath twining with yours, your forms a single shadow. \nBow your head. Offer your neck.", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T10:04:25.611000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1421437317155127306", "filename": "7.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1397030, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421437317155127306/7.jpg?ex=69cceda9&is=69cb9c29&hm=d77ccfb45aef3280439ea0a33850bb08c81af71dbdb316132ca9190a4b5998f9&"}, {"id": "1421437317490675732", "filename": "7.-She_Offers_Her_Neck-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 37626964, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421437317490675732/7.-She_Offers_Her_Neck-.wav?ex=69cceda9&is=69cb9c29&hm=43d3f92da87272ab5ab29a569de02901d528a52498653f8e28033c60cb2eda11&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1421435867402338375", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：畸变丰穰之种", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1421437442116030535", "channel_id": "1421435867402338375", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**08.眼-Her Eyes-**\n\n请闭眼，让吻落在指间。\n因她对你如此倾心，因漫长的旅程或会使你疲惫，却不会使你犹疑。\n\nClose your eyes, and let her kiss fall upon your fingertips. \nFor she is so deeply devoted to you. The long journey may weary you, but it will never make you hesitate.", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T10:04:55.231000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1421437440970719262", "filename": "8.-Her_Eyes-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 27472612, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421437440970719262/8.-Her_Eyes-.wav?ex=69ccedc6&is=69cb9c46&hm=d154d6179f58b5ae5605fd7e975d8449742adec0274c6126c607461cecde1fd9&"}, {"id": "1421437441650331711", "filename": "8.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1357475, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421437441650331711/8.jpg?ex=69ccedc7&is=69cb9c47&hm=aacef6ab2f4d3e2df626b685b7814ef26cf367e96f265ca770491d5f8df9a68a&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1421435867402338375", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：畸变丰穰之种", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1421437615202238464", "channel_id": "1421435867402338375", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**09.银沙海之舞-Dance of the Silver Sands-**\n\n她在沙中踏出黑色涟漪，她牵引你、捉住你，把种种从荒芜中托寄给你。\n今晚的月亮遮掩了一个华美晦涩的秘密，她既在舞中解答你的疑惑，也以一舞留给你更多谜题。\n\nShe steps into the sand, creating black ripples. She leads you, she holds you, entrusting you with all that rises from the barren. \nTonight, the moon conceals a grand, obscure secret. With one dance, she answers your questions and leaves you with a greater mystery.", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T10:05:36.498000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1421437614254461080", "filename": "9.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1411855, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421437614254461080/9.jpg?ex=69ccedf0&is=69cb9c70&hm=964992628bba6ab5710273eff7ffc90e9bda42b50250ab7eff6b787cc27516bb&"}, {"id": "1421437614782681168", "filename": "9.-Dance_of_the_Silver_Sands-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 21759998, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421437614782681168/9.-Dance_of_the_Silver_Sands-.wav?ex=69ccedf0&is=69cb9c70&hm=ff58d07c27ca80d627687235c46c7ff7554c6cfdbdbce9a4f6290a9dbf7b1e26&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1421435867402338375", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：畸变丰穰之种", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1421437756785295421", "channel_id": "1421435867402338375", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**10.风暴之壁-The Stormy Wall-**\n\n溯源之途，以生命垒砌，向它咆哮，抵御不可违背的伟力。将血脉还于亚兰，将丰穰还于亚兰！\n\nThe path to reclaiming our blood's origin is paved with countless lives. Roar against it! Resist the inevitable destruction! Return our bloodline to Aram! Return abundance to Aram!", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T10:06:10.254000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1421437755988246590", "filename": "10.-The_Stormy_Wall-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 49677722, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421437755988246590/10.-The_Stormy_Wall-.wav?ex=69ccee12&is=69cb9c92&hm=0a11f13935376bcc27c700c76ffb8cdc69e2af7f65ada344f4563ac61708b9ae&"}, {"id": "1421437756848078889", "filename": "10.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1393782, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421437756848078889/10.jpg?ex=69ccee12&is=69cb9c92&hm=b199981e99ce2b5da3007d7ace58fbc33e6ca2fd410339d286a1540d5a7a03fd&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1421435867402338375", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：畸变丰穰之种", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1421437928093257739", "channel_id": "1421435867402338375", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**11.归向海-Toward the Sea-**\n\n时间、生息、虚无、命运。\n所有晦涩的梦境，空茫的现实，平等地汇进洪流，消若无迹，一往无前，往海中去。\n\nTime, vitality, nothingness, destiny. \nAll obscure dreams, all empty realities... They flow equally into the great torrent, disappearing without a trace, moving ever onward, toward the sea.", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T10:06:51.097000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1421437927808041020", "filename": "11.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1379948, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421437927808041020/11.jpg?ex=69ccee3b&is=69cb9cbb&hm=9164c9096af0024544b2cdf0613be5840cb0744e03d9cee09d9a99b8368f3051&"}, {"id": "1421437928130740256", "filename": "11.-Toward_the_Sea-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 28507154, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421437928130740256/11.-Toward_the_Sea-.wav?ex=69ccee3b&is=69cb9cbb&hm=4d99838108aa031077b2608eac6d608908c42e5c2cbfd7ef4d524cbc95e735da&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1421435867402338375", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：畸变丰穰之种", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1421438048834687042", "channel_id": "1421435867402338375", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**12.先驱者的丧钟-Toll of the Forerunner-**\n\n近了，那死的神灵，终的吐息，传奇但未为众知的过往，凝窒而轻描淡写的别离。\n\nThey draw near: the god of death, the final breath, a legendary but untold past, a stifled and understated farewell.", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T10:07:19.884000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1421438048020987996", "filename": "12.-Toll_of_the_Forerunner-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 26593018, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421438048020987996/12.-Toll_of_the_Forerunner-.wav?ex=69ccee57&is=69cb9cd7&hm=159f181cfe0df8f69235a81568f454a8cb3f850abbfcf76760534db73dc9734e&"}, {"id": "1421438048561922058", "filename": "12.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1409593, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421438048561922058/12.jpg?ex=69ccee57&is=69cb9cd7&hm=43eb2dc1f64ea7207de7fa8513497d04876fbedbf816d11420911665afb6ba3e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1421435867402338375", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：畸变丰穰之种", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1421438229969768539", "channel_id": "1421435867402338375", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**13.无声神谕-The Silent Oracle-**\n\n自她口中降下的，是神谕抑或王旨，是天恩抑或私心。\n树魂与傀儡共鸣，许诺她永恒孤独的空寂。\n\nFrom her lips fall an oracle or a royal decree, divine grace or selfish whim. \nThe soul of Mother Tree resonates with its puppet, promising her an eternal and solitary emptiness.", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T10:08:03.070000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1421438229357527170", "filename": "13.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1388681, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421438229357527170/13.jpg?ex=69ccee82&is=69cb9d02&hm=0f8a07dd0701063ee1c1311d3b1e6eabac57e4426805cbec9d85ecb097f15454&"}, {"id": "1421438229609054349", "filename": "13.-The_Silent_Oracle-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 3220418, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421438229609054349/13.-The_Silent_Oracle-.mp3?ex=69ccee82&is=69cb9d02&hm=8b0abd15a479214a50d5b777b0c99b914462d8ad24b5201f6e8a2656555565f1&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1421435867402338375", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：畸变丰穰之种", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1421438585709527060", "channel_id": "1421435867402338375", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**14.为已逝者-For the Departed-**\n\n我已遗忘祂的身形，我已遗忘祂的名姓。\n但我将抛却私心，我愿化为银蚁，待祂归返，待祂重临。\n待她将我拥入怀中，待她否认那声叹息。\n\nI have forgotten Her form. I have forgotten Her name. But I will cast away my own desires. I will become a silver ant, waiting for Her return, waiting for Her arrival. \nWaiting for her arms to hold me; waiting for her to deny that sigh.", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T10:09:27.885000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1421438584568807516", "filename": "14.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1388830, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421438584568807516/14.jpg?ex=69cceed7&is=69cb9d57&hm=cc1be05d7e6bee203a1937fcf42b5760dee208ac1662269e95b94cfefdafcbe1&"}, {"id": "1421438585113940038", "filename": "14.-For_the_Departed-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 2220660, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421438585113940038/14.-For_the_Departed-.mp3?ex=69cceed7&is=69cb9d57&hm=425fd4ea76ff7ff236c09582ecf8d790464abe60525d2f51d063747ccaa69867&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1421435867402338375", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：畸变丰穰之种", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1421438959665283124", "channel_id": "1421435867402338375", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**16.百年见证-Centuries of Witness-**\n\n女王的肉身被融蚀侵袭，亚兰的子民在黄沙中流亡。\n光阴从缝隙间被见证，由故去者，见证命运未能奈何亚兰的数百年。\n\nThe Queen's flesh is Dissoluted, and the people of Aram wander the desert in exile. \nFrom the gaps in time, the departed bear witness to the centuries that fate could not claim Aram.", "timestamp": "2025-09-27T10:10:57.043000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1421438958969032854", "filename": "16.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1385451, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421438958969032854/16.jpg?ex=69ccef30&is=69cb9db0&hm=0716321d14b653e0638c47d76f1ba92b2b93ab331e1c5a046fe770f60a6ec601&"}, {"id": "1421438959292121128", "filename": "16.-Centuries_of_Witness-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 35448074, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1421435867402338375/1421438959292121128/16.-Centuries_of_Witness-.wav?ex=69ccef30&is=69cb9db0&hm=d7b7301523871015ff584f0a5cffeb78a453428b90c8b0b21ce2aafeeda301ef&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1421435867402338375", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：畸变丰穰之种", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
